Cordillera del Cóndor region. Río Machinaza watershed, east of Los Encuentros. Refugio de Vida Silvestre El Zarza. 0.25-hectare forest inventory plot, Aurelian Plot 10. Cordillera del Cóndor region, upper Río Nangaritza. Las Orquídeas reserve, on west side of river. Tall, primary forest on steep slope above river, below sandstone plateau but with soil mostly derived from eroded sandstone. Canopy to 30 m with Chrysophyllum sanguineolentum dominant. One-hectare forest inventory plot; all trees > 10 cm DBH sampled, during dendrology course with students from Ecuador and Peru, funded by US National Science Foundation. Nangaritza River Plot.
